1.0.name: wordpress/wp-e-commerce-table-price-shortcode
1.0.description:
This plugin adds a shortcode for use with the WordPress e-Commerce Plugin. Use the [wpsc_table_price] shortcode where you want to display the table rate prices for a product. This plugin can save you time and energy when you update your table prices.

Developer Website: http://MyWebsiteAdvisor.com/

Plugin Support: http://MyWebsiteAdvisor.com/support/

Plugin Page: http://MyWebsiteAdvisor.com/tools/wordpress-plugins/wp-e-commerce-table-price-shortcode/

Premium Version with Advanced Features including:

  • Customize Shortcode Output
  • Automatically Detect Product ID when used on Prod
